  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Protective Antenna Kit",
      "text": "The MikroTik Sleeve30 Kit (MPN: Sleeve30) is specifically designed for MikroTik mANT30 parabolic antennas, providing additional protection, durability, and improved performance in demanding outdoor conditions. By shielding the antenna feed, the sleeve minimizes the impact of environmental factors such as snow, rain, dust, and UV radiation, helping extend the lifespan of your equipment while maintaining consistent signal stability. It also reduces unwanted signal interference, ensuring better link quality and overall efficiency in long-distance wireless deployments. Beyond its functional advantages, the sleeve enhances the antenna’s durability and appearance, making it more resilient in harsh environments. Installation is straightforward and does not require special tools or advanced technical knowledge, allowing for quick and secure setup. Whether used in urban, rural, or coastal deployments, the MikroTik Sleeve30 Kit is a cost-effective solution for ensuring reliable performance and long-term protection of your mANT30 antennas."
    }
